label: exporterInfo
comment: Personal information of the organization exporting the commodity corresponding to this observation.

label: consignerInfo
comment: Details of the consignor sending the shipment corresponding to this observation.

label: consigneeInfo
comment: Details of the consignee receiving the shipment corresponding to this observation.

label: rcmcInfo
comment: Detailed information about the RCMC (Registration-cum-membership-certificate) issued by Export Promotion Council.

label: phytosanitaryInfo
comment: Details of the phytosanitary certificate issued by the competent authority. These certificates are used to attest that consignments meet phytosanitary import requirements and are undertaken by a National Plant Protection Organization

label: fssaiInfo
comment: The FSSAI (Food and Safety Standards Authority of India) license details corresponding to this observation.

label: originName
comment: The name of the origin location corresponding to this observation.

label: destinationName
comment: The name of the destination location corresponding to this observation.

label: originCode
comment: The code of the origin location corresponding to this observation.

label: destinationCode
comment: The code of the destination location corresponding to this observation.

label: portOfShipment
comment: The port where the consignment has been shipped from.

label: portOfEntry
comment: The port where the consignment will land in the country of destination.

label: shipmentDate
comment: The date on which the commodity is expected to leave the port of shipment.

label: consignmentNumber
comment: The unique alphanumeric assigned to the consignment procedure in order to track it.

label: packageDescription
comment: The distinguishing identification marks or description of the packaging of merchandise / commodity corresponding to this observation.

label: vesselName
comment: The name of the vessel that carries the consignment.

label: consignmentQuantity
comment: The number of units or weight of cargo or food involved in the consignment corresponding to this observation.

label: natureOfConsignment
comment: Describes whether the consignment is a sample or the actual merchandise.

label: sanitaryMeasures
comment: Describes the type of disinfection treatment applied to the consignment.

label: capitalInfo
comment: The income and expenditure information corresponding to the entity.

label: insuranceInfo
comment: The information about the insurance for the product or equipment or service corresponding to this observation.

label: mediaURL
comment: Link(s) to any image(s) or media of the entity or incident corresponding to this observation

label: commodityInfo
comment: The information about the agricultural produce/commodity associated with the amc/market corresponding to this observation.

label: validTill
comment: The specific period of time during which a document, authorization, offer or permission remains legally or effectively acceptable/applicable.

label: insurancePremium
comment: The amount that is paid by the individual or business for availing the insurance policy.

label: fob
comment: FOB (Free On Board) refers to the ownership and risk associated with shipping goods corresponding to this observation.
